# Markman CLI Bookmark Manager

@id: CLI_BOOKMARKS
@status: draft
@priority: medium
@depends: []

## Overview

A CLI tool for managing web bookmarks with tagging and search.

## Requirements

### Add Bookmark

Add a URL with optional tags and description.

### Search Bookmarks

Search bookmarks by tag, title, or URL substring.

## Acceptance Criteria

- `markman add <url>` stores a new bookmark
- `markman search <query>` finds matching bookmarks
